{{infobox country at games | NOC = GBS | NOCname = Comité Olímpico da Guiné&#x2011;Bissau | games = Olympics | year = | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = | location = | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = {{Team appearances list|team=Guinea-Bissau|competition=Summer Olympics|begin_year=1996|end_year= }} | winterappearances = | seealso = }} '''[[Guinea-Bissau]]''' has sent athletes to every [[Summer Olympic Games]] held since [[1996 Summer Olympics|1996]], although the country has never won an [[Olympic Games#Olympic champions and medalists|Olympic medal]]. No athletes from Guinea-Bissau have competed in any [[Winter Olympic Games]].
The [[National Olympic Committee]] was created in 1992 and recognized by the [[International Olympic Committee]] in 1995.
